Title: Red Dead Redemption II
Description: Amidst the decline of the Wild West at the turn of the 20th century, outlaw Arthur Morgan and his gang struggle to cope with the loss of their way of life.

Title: The Last of Us
Description: In a hostile, post-pandemic world, Joel and Ellie, brought together by desperate circumstances, must rely on each other to survive a brutal journey across what remains of the United States.

Title: Wiedzmin 3: Dziki Gon
Description: The monster slayer Geralt of Rivia must find his adoptive daughter who is being pursued by the Wild Hunt, and prevent the White Frost from bringing about the end of the world.

Title: Baldur's Gate III
Description: Return to Faerun in a tale of fellowship and betrayal, and the lure of absolute power. Mysterious abilities are awakening inside you. Resist, and turn darkness against itself. Or embrace corruption, and become ultimate evil.

Title: Metal Gear Solid
Description: A crack government anti-terrorist squad takes over an obscure Alaskan nuclear disposal facility. Solid Snake is up for the task to infiltrate the facility, rescue the two hostages and thwart the terrorists' plans.

Title: The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time
Description: A young Kokiri boy discovers that his destiny is to free the Seven Sages and save the land of Hyrule from the treacherous sorcerer Ganondorf.

Title: God of War: Ragnarök
Description: Kratos and his son Atreus face the oncoming Norse apocalypse, Ragnarok.

Title: Grand Theft Auto V
Description: Three very different criminals team up for a series of heists and walk into some of the most thrilling experiences in the corrupt city of Los Santos.

Title: Uncharted 4: A Thief's End
Description: Thrown back into the dangerous underworld he'd tried to leave behind, Nathan Drake must decide what he's willing to sacrifice to save the ones he loves.

Title: God of War
Description: After wiping out the gods of Mount Olympus, Kratos moves on to the frigid lands of Scandinavia, where he and his son must embark on an odyssey across a dangerous world of gods and monsters.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Tiâzu obu za kingudamu
Description: When Link and princess Zelda investigate Zonai ruins in a cave beneath the castle, they witness the awakening of a mummified Ganondorf, whose powers then corrupt Link's arm, after which Hyrule Castle is sent floating upward into the sky.

Title: Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater
Description: In 1964, a U.S. government operative codenamed "Snake" must infiltrate mountainous Soviet territory to rescue a scientist building a weapon of terrible power.

Title: Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic
Description: A republic soldier, training to become a Jedi Knight, is given the task of halting the conquest of Darth Malak by discovering the location of a weapon known as the Star Forge.

Title: Mass Effect 2
Description: After being revived from death and having to join a pro-human organization without a choice, Commander Shepard must assemble a team, battle a new threat, and make tough choices in order to save the galaxy from total annihilation once more.

Title: Fainaru fantajî VII
Description: A former soldier from an evil company joins a mercenary clan to fight the company he once served.

Title: Chrono Trigger
Description: Crono, a young boy, is thrust to adventure by destiny to destroy an oncoming threat that will destroy the world in 1999.

Title: Bloodborne: The Old Hunters
Description: In this DLC for Bloodborne (2015), the player-Hunter is transported to the sinister Hunter's Nightmare, a demented place where hunters who become drunk with blood are sent to.

Title: Alan Wake II
Description: 13 years after bestselling writer Alan Wake went missing, a string of ritualistic murders occur in the town of Bright Falls, Washington. Saga Anderson, an FBI agent, is sent to Bright Falls to investigate the murders.

Title: Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas
Description: Carl "CJ" Johnson, a member of the Grove Street street gang, comes home after a family tragedy to find it overtaken by crime and corruption, which he must take back before things become worse.

Title: Cyberpunk 2077: Phantom Liberty
Description: Phantom Liberty is a new spy-thriller adventure for Cyberpunk 2077. Return as cyber-enhanced mercenary V and embark on a high-stakes mission of espionage and intrigue to save the NUS President.

Title: Red Dead Redemption
Description: A former outlaw is forced by the federal government to hunt down the members of his old gang.

Title: Elden Ring
Description: In a dark fantasy world created by Hidetaka Miyazaki (Dark Souls) and George R. R. Martin (A Song of Ice and Fire), the player is a Tarnished who is called back to the Lands Between to restore the Elden Ring and become the Elden Lord.

Title: Resident Evil 4
Description: In this HD remake of the 2005 game, Leon Kennedy is sent on a mission to rescue the president's kidnapped daughter from a secluded European village where there is something terribly wrong with the locals.

Title: Batman: Arkham City
Description: When part of Gotham is turned into a private reserve for criminals known as Arkham City, all hell is sure to break loose, and the Dark Knight is the only one who can stop it.

Title: Half-Life 2
Description: Dr. Freeman is taken out of stasis by his "employer" to help rid the planet of invading aliens forces known as the Combine that entered through the portals he helped create.

Title: Portal 2
Description: Many years after "Portal," Chell reawakens at Aperture Science and tries to stop GLaDOS once again with the help of Wheatley, who has his own plans for the historical facility.

Title: Silent Hill 2
Description: After receiving a letter from his late wife, from Silent Hill, James Sunderland heads towards the town to search for her, only to come across a terrifying road of truth and redemption.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Buresu obu za wairudo
Description: After a century of hibernation, Link reawakens to once again save a ruined Hyrule from a great evil.

Title: Forgotten Realms: Baldur's Gate II - Shadows of Amn
Description: Jon Irenicus, a sadistic secretive powerful mage bent on revenge, captures Gorion's ward and his/her party for a diabolical experiment.

Title: Metal Gear Solid 4: Guns of the Patriots
Description: When the nations of the world rely upon private military companies to fight their battles for them, renegade Liquid Ocelot emerges as the head of a potent coalition of mercenary powers. Solid Snake returns to save the world once again.

Title: Fallout 2: A Post-Nuclear Role-Playing Game
Description: In a post-nuclear future, the descendant of an ancient exiled hero must leave his tribe in search of the Garden of Eden Creation Kit, the last chance of survival for his people.

Title: Planescape: Torment
Description: In the city of Sigil, the only place from which all realities of the Planescape universe can be reached, an immortal amnesiac, the Nameless One, must uncover his past, the mystery of his immortality as well as who's trying to kill him.

Title: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim
Description: After escaping execution, the last living Dragonborn must grow in strength and power to defeat the dragons that have once again begun to plague the land of Skyrim.

Title: Spider-Man 2
Description: Spider-Men, Peter Parker and Miles Morales, return for an exciting new adventure in the critically acclaimed Marvel's Spider-Man franchise.

Title: Bloodborne
Description: A hunter awakens in the plagued lands of Yharnam, where the denizens have succumb to beast hood, in an attempt to learn the truth and how to end the plague, unbeknownst of the true horror lurking within the city.

Title: Uncharted 2: Among Thieves
Description: After being tracked down by Harry Flynn, Nathan Drake goes on a quest for Marco Polo's lost fleet. However when things take an unexpected turn for the worst, Drake must rely on those closest to him in order to find the Cintomani Stone.

Title: P.T.
Description: The player must navigate a series of continuously looping hallways, solving cryptic puzzles, all while being hunted by a hostile apparition named Lisa.

Title: The Secret of Monkey Island
Description: Young pirate wanna-be Guybrush Threepwood sets out to pass the Three Trials, woo the governess Elaine Marley, reach the fabled Monkey Island and vanquish the nefarious ghost pirate LeChuck.

Title: Kingdom Hearts II
Description: Sora and friends face mysterious new enemies as they continue their journey to save all worlds, and find Riku and King Mickey.

Title: Detroit: Become Human
Description: Take control of three androids in their quest to discover who they really are.

Title: Spider-Man
Description: When a new villain threatens New York City, Peter Parker and Spider-Man's worlds collide. To save the city and those he loves, he must rise up and be greater.

Title: Ghost of Tsushima
Description: Set in 1274 on the Tsushima Island, the last samurai, Jin Sakai, must master a new fighting style, the way of the Ghost, to defeat the Mongol forces and fight for the freedom and independence of Japan.

Title: Grand Theft Auto: Vice City
Description: After being released from jail, Tommy Vercetti leaves Liberty City for Vice City, a city overrun by the mob. Now, Tommy is out to make Vice City his home.

Title: Max Payne
Description: A troubled NYPD cop is framed for murder and finds himself being hunted by the police, the mob, and a ruthless corporation.

Title: God of War II
Description: After being betrayed by the gods of Olympus and annulled of his divine powers, Kratos must embark on a journey to meet the Sisters of Fate and take his revenge on Olympus.

Title: Biohazard 4
Description: Six years after the events in Raccoon City, Leon Kennedy, now a federal agent, is sent to a rural part of Spain to rescue the U.S. President's kidnapped daughter, Ashley Graham from a sinister cult.

Title: The Walking Dead: The Game - Season 1
Description: In a world devastated by the undead, a convicted criminal is given a second chance at life when he comes across a little girl named Clementine.

Title: Half-Life
Description: Dr. Gordon Freeman must fight his way out of a secret research facility after a teleportation experiment goes disastrously wrong.

Title: Deus Ex
Description: In a dark cyberpunk future where poverty, disease, oppression and terrorism are widespread, J.C. Denton, a new cybernetically-enhanced special agent, finds evidence of a massive conspiracy when his brother, also an agent, goes rogue.

Title: Kingdom Hearts
Description: When his world is destroyed and his friends mysteriously disappear, a young boy named Sora is thrust into a quest to find his missing friends and prevent the armies of darkness from destroying many other worlds.

Title: Persona 5
Description: A group of high school students create a vigilante group to expose the crimes of corrupt adults but soon find themselves in the midst of a worldwide conspiracy and targeted by powerful individuals who would do anything to silence them.

Title: Fallout
Description: After being sent by the overseer of his vault to search for a new water purifying chip, the player discovers the horrors of post apocalyptic America, and the threat of the Master's Army.

Title: Batman: Return to Arkham
Description: Batman: Return to Arkham thrusts players back into the environments of Arkham Asylum and Arkham City with a remastered graphics engine and all DLC.

Title: Grim Fandango
Description: Manuel Calavera is a travel agent in The Land of the Dead who has stumbled across a ring of corruption.

Title: Super Mario World
Description: While Mario and Luigi are vacationing in Dinosaur Land, Bowser kidnaps the Princess. Mario and his new dino friend Yoshi go on a mission to save her.

Title: Akumajo Dracula X: Gekka no Yasokyoku
Description: Richter Belmont has vanished just as Castlevania reemerged from the mists. Meanwhile, Alucard, the bastard son of Dracula, has awakened from his eternal slumber, intent on destroying his evil father once and for all.

Title: Wanda to kyozô
Description: A young man brings a deceased woman to a forbidden land inhabited by colossal beings said to house the power to revive the dead.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Kamigami no toraifôsu
Description: The wizard Agahnim has abducted seven maidens, intent on using their power to open a portal to the Dark World. Armed with a trusty sword and shield, Link begins a great and treacherous journey.

Title: Persona 4
Description: A high school student forms a group that explores a hidden world accessible through TV sets to find a connection between the "realm of shadows" and the mysterious murders in their town.

Title: Super Mario Bros. 3
Description: King Koopa has kidnapped Princess Toadstool, taken over all seven kingdoms in the Mushroom World, and put his seven kids in charge of all of them. It's the Mario Brothers to the rescue.

Title: Monkey Island 2: LeChuck's Revenge
Description: Having vanquished the ghost pirate LeChuck with a soft drink, Guybrush Threepwood now seeks the treasure of Big Whoop. During his quest he discovers LeChuck is back from the dead. Once again.

Title: Mass Effect
Description: In a technologically advanced future, an elite human soldier takes command of a prototype star ship and works to defend the galaxy from danger.

Title: God of War III
Description: Armed with his deadly double-chained blades, Kratos must take on Greek mythology's darkest creatures to destroy Olympus and the mighty Zeus himself.

Title: It Takes Two
Description: The clashing couple Cody and May are turned into dolls by a magic book. Together, trapped in a fantastical world where the unpredictable hides around every corner, they are reluctantly challenged with saving their fractured relationship.

Title: Batman: Arkham Asylum
Description: Batman battles his archenemy, the Joker, who instigates an elaborate plot to seize control of Arkham Asylum, trap Batman inside with many of his incarcerated foes, and threaten Gotham City with hidden bombs.

Title: Max Payne 2: The Fall of Max Payne
Description: The brooding cop has left the DEA and returned to the NYPD. When his latest case ends up involving the thought-dead femme fatale Mona Sax, he finds that his journey through the night is far from over.

Title: Fallout 3
Description: Centuries following nuclear war, a teen leaves the safety of an underground vault in order to find their father, who left in hopes of creating a water purifier.

Title: BioShock Infinite
Description: A man is sent to the flying city of Columbia to find a missing girl. However, upon arrival he discovers that the city, its people, and his objective are all not what they seem.

Title: Mass Effect 3
Description: Earth is under attack by a monstrous race of gigantic living ships known as the Reapers. Even if Commander Shepard could unite all surviving species in the galaxy, only a miracle could save them. Then again, Shepard did come back from the dead.

Title: BioShock
Description: In 1960, a lone survivor of a plane crash named Jack discovers an abandoned underwater utopia, only to find out that the mystery behind its creation is much more sinister than he first believed.

Title: Dragon Age: Origins
Description: After four hundred years since the last Blight, a new Archdemon seeks to destroy the land of Ferelden. It is up to the player - as one of the remaining Grey Wardens - to unite the divided armies of Ferelden and save humanity.

Title: Disco Elysium
Description: You're a detective tasked with solving a murder in the strange world of Elysium. Utilize a new and innovative skill system to be the detective you want to be. Become a hero or an absolute disaster of a human being.

Title: Dark Souls
Description: After narrowly escaping a doomed fate in an asylum, an undead warrior fights his way through the desolate remains of Lordran, once a sprawling utopia lead by the gods, to seek his purpose and fulfill a centuries old prophecy.

Title: Fainaru fantajî X
Description: A celebrated young athlete is drawn from his futuristic hometown and convenient lifestyle to a harsh and techno-phobic land by a mysterious force only known as Sin.

Title: Dark Souls III
Description: The fire is fading. Darkness creeps across the land. The Lords of Cinder charged with watching over the First Flame have abandoned their thrones. The Champion of Ash, an undead is chosen to return them to their thrones.

Title: Super Mario 64
Description: When the evil Bowser steals 120 power stars and traps Princess Peach within the walls of her own castle, it's up to Mario to save her once again.

Title: Mafia: The City of Lost Heaven
Description: You play a 1930s mobster as you act out your confession of your rise in the ranks of organized crime.

Title: Biohazard 2
Description: Two months after the mansion events, the deadly T-virus escapes into the streets of Raccoon City. Leon Kennedy and Claire Redfield find the police office left abandoned. In an underground facility the story of Umbrella Corp. gets unfolded.

Title: Portal
Description: A test subject wakes up in a scientific facility controlled by a sadistic artificial intelligence and must escape with the help of the only instrument she has--a gun that makes portals.

Title: GoldenEye 007
Description: James Bond must track down agent-turned-terrorist Alec Trevelyan to stop the launch of a powerful satellite. Play the game that set the stage for the First-person shooter genre on the console.

Title: Super Mario Odyssey
Description: Mario must travel to worlds unknown in order to stop Bowser from marrying Princess Peach.

Title: Final Fantasy VI
Description: A mysterious woman joins a group of mercenaries in order to find out about her destiny and means of saving the world from an evil madman.

Title: Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines
Description: Beginning your journey as a new Kindred, you must choose your path to follow the high class Vampire Society, or the lawbreaking group of Anarchs as you find your place in this new world.

Title: Super Mario Galaxy
Description: When Princess Peach is abducted as part of Bowser's galaxy creation scheme, stalwart plumber Mario must leap to her rescue, with the help of new celestial friends and powers.

Title: Half-Life 2: Episode Two
Description: Gordon Freeman, along with the help of human and non-human allies, continues his fight against the ruthless alien force known as the Combine.

Title: StarCraft
Description: In 2499 in the Koprulu sector, a ferocious collective race known as the Zerg arrives to massacre the exiled human colonies while a highly advanced race, the Protoss, intervenes to exterminate the Zerg.

Title: The Curse of Monkey Island
Description: After unwittingly turning his true love Elaine into solid gold with a cursed engagement ring, Guybrush Threepwood must find a map, a ship and a crew, sail to Blood Island and track down an uncursed diamond ring to reverse the curse.

Title: Super Metroid
Description: Samus Aran returns to the brooding planet Zebes to recover the last metroid from the Space Pirates.

Title: Metal Gear: Ghost Babel
Description: In this non-canonical sequel to Metal Gear Solid, Solid Snake is called upon from his home in Alaska to infiltrate an enemy base searching for Metal Gear.

Title: Batman: Arkham Knight
Description: With his back against the wall, Batman turns to his closest allies to help him save Gotham City from the clutches of Scarecrow and the Arkham Knight's army. A familiar face also returns to give The Dark Knight a message he cannot ignore.

Title: Star Wars Jedi: Survivor
Description: The story of Cal Kestis continues in STAR WARS Jedi: Survivor, a galaxy-spanning, third-person, action-adventure game.

Title: God of War
Description: After 10 years of endless nightmares and servitude to the gods of Olympus, Kratos is assigned with a final task, to kill Ares, the God of War.

Title: Horizon: Forbidden West
Description: Aloy treks into an arcane region and faces new hostile enemies and threats in search of a way to heal the world from a deadly blight and catastrophic storms.

Title: Resident Evil 2
Description: Re-imagining of Biohazard 2 (1998), with a third-person over-the-shoulder view, new details, rearranged and new areas, no more loading screen doors, new puzzle solving opportunities, a gunpowder crafting mechanic and more.

Title: Assassin's Creed II
Description: Desmond Miles is trained to become a modern-day Assassin through the resurrected memories of ancestor Ezio Auditore da Firenze, who uncovers a massive Templar conspiracy in Renaissance Italy leading to the new Pope.

Title: Horizon Zero Dawn
Description: In a primitive tribal world where strange, monstrous, animalistic machines roam the wilderness, a brave young female warrior goes on a quest to learn the truth about her mysterious origin and the state the world is in.

Title: Silent Hill
Description: Harry awakes from a car crash to notice his daughter, Cheryl, vanished. As he searches for her, through the eerie town of Silent Hill, a terrifying descent into the unknown is set.

Title: Call of Duty 4: Modern Warfare
Description: The Call of Duty series returns this time into a modern day setting. The player takes control of a character nicknamed "Soap," for the majority of the campaign and will need to progress through many modern warfare scenarios.

Title: Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty
Description: Two years after the death of Solid Snake, a rookie FOX-HOUND agent, on his first mission, infiltrates an offshore decontamination facility to rescue the President.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Mujura no kamen
Description: After becoming the hero of Hyrule, Link stumbles into the enchanted land of Termina, where a falling moon will crush the world in three days.

Title: Biohazard
Description: Remake of the first game in which the RPD squad, Jill and Chris, are forced to flee into a mysterious mansion. Featuring new gameplay mechanics, revised puzzles, additional explorable areas, a revised script, and new story details.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu Towairaito purinsesu
Description: Link, a young man from a small farming village, finds Hyrule is being consumed by an otherworldly twilight. Guided by a strange pixie named Midna, he endeavors to return light to the land and confront the usurper king Zant.

Title: Uncharted 3: L'inganno di Drake
Description: Treasure hunter Nathan Drake embarks on a quest in search of the Atlantis of the Sands while battling an ancient, sinister organization.

Title: Diablo II
Description: Evil has survived. Diablo, the Lord of Terror, now seeks to free his demonic brothers. The armies of the High Heavens are forbidden to interfere with Diablo's plan.

Title: Ori and the Will of the Wisps
Description: Ori begins a new journey that goes beyond the forest of Nibel where he uncovers lost secrets, and unearths his true destiny.

Title: Super Mario Galaxy 2
Description: Mario goes back in the galaxy to save Princess Peach from Bowser.

Title: Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis
Description: Indiana Jones must fight the nazis again in search for Atlantis and a newly discovered mineral of unbelievable power, the Orichalcum.

Title: Baldur's Gate II: Throne of Bhaal
Description: The main character, Gorion's ward, and his or her party must overcome five children of the dead god Bhaal, who've raised armies to conquer the world through carnage and claim their father's sinister throne and title.

Title: Day of the Tentacle
Description: A disembodied tentacle is accidentally exposed to nuclear waste, giving it human abilities and an ambition to take over the world.

Title: Shenmue
Description: Ryo, a respected Japanese student sees his father killed in front of his own eyes. He sets out to find the man in charge of his fathers death and the mystery of who and why?

Title: The Longest Journey
Description: April Ryan is a young visual-arts student in Venice, Newport. She's been having some strange dreams lately, but little does she know about the important role she'll have in changing the future.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Kaze no takuto
Description: After his sister gets kidnapped from their peaceful island, a young boy aims to emulate the Hero of Time by saving her.

Title: Heroes of Might and Magic III: The Restoration of Erathia
Description: Turn-based strategy game in which the player goes through 7 different campaigns, controlling a number of heroes that command an army of creatures inspired by myth and legend.

Title: StarCraft: Brood War
Description: After the events of StarCraft (1998) the Protoss try to unite their divided race while still fighting the weakened Zerg which is also attacked by human expedition from Earth.

Title: Fallout: New Vegas
Description: After surviving a bullet to the head, Courier Six traverses the post-apocalyptic Mojave desert in search of the men who wronged him, while making an impact on thousands in the process.

Title: Dead Space
Description: Set in the 26th century, the story follows engineer Isaac Clarke on a mission to repair the USG Ishimura, a mining spaceship that has been overrun by undead creatures called Necromorphs.

Title: Grand Theft Auto IV
Description: Niko Bellic comes to Liberty City, America to live the good life, but ends up having to assist his dangerously indebted cousin Roman with his financial troubles, by any (mostly illegal) means necessary.

Title: Life Is Strange
Description: An awkward photography student named Max discovers her ability to rewind time, and reunites with her estranged best friend Chloe to investigate the mysterious disappearance of a local girl.

Title: Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice
Description: Set in a reimagining of 1500s Sengoku era Japan. An unnamed shinobi, tasked with protecting a young lord of mystical lineage, who is left for dead when a powerful samurai attacks and chops off his arm.

Title: Resident Evil
Description: The RPD are investigating strange cannibalized corpses on the outskirts of the city. The Alpha squad, Jill and Chris, are sent to locate missing team members. While there, mutated dogs cause them to flee into a supposedly abandoned mansion.

Title: Ryû ga gotoku Zero: Chikai no basho
Description: Kiryu and Majima, both Yakuza's who are in different cities in Japan in 1988, as the fate of the two characters become intertwined in a gritty, violent, and often touching narrative.

Title: The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion
Description: After being freed by the Emperor of Tamriel, the hero must prevent the gates of Oblivion from spreading throughout the Empire.

Title: Hades
Description: Hades is a rogue-like dungeon crawler from the creators of Bastion and Transistor, in which you defy the god of death as you hack and slash your way out of the Underworld of Greek myth.

Title: The Wolf Among Us
Description: As Bigby Wolf, the big bad wolf in human form, you will discover that the brutal, bloody murder of a Fable is just a taste of things to come when another dead Fable is found which starts the hunt for a serial killer.

Title: Baldur's Gate
Description: The main character, ward of mystical monk Gorion, whose name, sex, race and class are defined by the players, leaves his order's keep for the first time and starts a journey to discover his true identity. But someone wants him dead.

Title: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate
Description: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate for the Nintendo Switch brings back every fighter in the history of the series, adds newcomers and over 100 stages, and introduces a new adventure mode called "World of Light''.

Title: South Park: The Stick of Truth
Description: As the New Kid, discover the lost Stick of Truth, and earn your place at the side of Stan, Kyle, Cartman and Kenny as their new friend.

Title: The Warriors
Description: The Warriors, a gang from Coney Island, go to a gang leader's meeting, when suddenly the gang leader is shot and killed. Framed for this murder, they must travel all the way back to Coney with 60,000 gang members standing in their way.

Title: Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II - The Sith Lords
Description: You play an exiled and depowered Jedi Knight who has returned to the Republic and must restore both your powers and the devastated Jedi Order to challenge the Sith.

Title: The Last of Us: Left Behind
Description: Find out what set Ellie on her course to the life changing events in The Last of Us (2013), whilst filling in the gaps during winter with Joel.

Title: Metal Gear Solid: The Twin Snakes
Description: A retired mercenary is called upon by the U.S. government to handle a hostile takeover of an Alaskan military base by his former special forces group. A remake of Metal Gear Solid (1998).

Title: Warcraft III: Reign of Chaos
Description: Years after the fall of the Orcish Horde to the human Alliance of Lordaeron, the remaining humans and orcs find themselves facing a common enemy: the demons of the Burning Legion and their armies of undead monsters.

Title: Super Mario Bros.
Description: A plumber named Mario and his brother Luigi travel through the Mushroom Kingdom to save the princess from the evil Bowser.

Title: Warcraft III: The Frozen Throne
Description: Survivors in the reign of chaos try to resolve their differences in a new world, that was shaped after the fall of the Burning Legion.

Title: Mother 2: Gîgu no gyakushuu
Description: Ness, a boy from Onett, Eagleland, teams up with new friends to defeat an Evil Destroyer named Giygas. During the epic pursuits, Ness and his allies attempt to find the sacred Eight Melodies.

Title: System Shock 2
Description: An agent is deployed on a mission to explore a distant planet, but instead wakes up from his cryosleep five months later only to discover that the ship's artificial intelligence has been corrupted and the humans infected by an alien race.

Title: The Last of Us: Part II
Description: Five years after the events of The Last of Us, Ellie embarks on another journey through a post-apocalyptic America on a mission of vengeance against a mysterious militia.

Title: Broken Sword: The Shadow of the Templars
Description: George Stobbart, an American tourist in Paris, attempts to unravel a conspiracy when he witnesses a bomb attack on a small Parisian cafe.

Title: Final Fantasy XVI
Description: As a malady known as the Blight ravages the land of Valisthea and its realms plunge into war, Clive Rosfield, the firstborn son of the Archduke of Rosaria, sets out on a dark, dangerous journey to revenge following a tragedy.

Title: Far Cry 3
Description: While skydiving, Jason Brody and his friends land on an island overrun by pirates, where Jason is torn between fighting for the Rakyat resistance and rescuing his friends.

Title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2
Description: A massacre at a Russian airport leads to a war between Russia and the United States. Meanwhile, a Task Force is sent to find the perpetrators and bring the bloodshed to an end.

Title: Divinity: Original Sin II
Description: Set in a fantasy world where a form of energy known as Source, and individuals called Sourcerers can manipulate this energy, are hunting down an organization to protect their world from the evil Voidwokens who are drawn by that energy.

Title: Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain
Description: After awakening from a nine year coma, Big Boss forms a new mercenary group called, Diamond Dogs, and teams up with his former rival, Ocelot, to track down the men responsible for the destruction of MSF.

Title: NieR: Automata
Description: In the forsaken wasteland below, the war between the machines and the androids rages on. A war that is soon to unveil the long-forgotten truth of this world.

Title: Heavy Rain
Description: As a child goes missing, his father tirelessly works to rescue him, while a journalist, an FBI agent, and a private detective try to identify his kidnapper known only as the "Origami Killer".

Title: Undertale
Description: Enter the Underground, a massive subterranean cave where monsters who once lived harmoniously with humans on the surface have been banished after losing a war with humanity.

Title: Halo 3
Description: Master Chief and the Arbiter must join together to attack the Covenant and destroy the Flood.

Title: Hollow Knight
Description: In a world of insects, a diminutive knight descends into an ancient and crazed kingdom to restore its fallen king's order.

Title: Dead Space
Description: Engineer Isaac Clarke and his crew get stranded on a large, abandoned mining ship. There, Clarke needs to repair the giant ship while battling nasty aliens and solving the mystery of what happened to the ship.

Title: Halo: Combat Evolved
Description: Super-soldier John-117, Master Chief of the United Nations Space Command, must battle a genocidal alien race known as the Covenant following his violent crash-landing on Halo, an ancient and mysterious ring-world.

Title: Tales from the Borderlands: A Telltale Games Series
Description: Corporate stooge Rhys, and Con woman Fiona team up to discover the secret of an alien vault on the dangerous planet Pandora.

Title: The Walking Dead: The Final Season
Description: Clementine and her adoptive brother, AJ, come across a boarding school inhabited by other children with little memory of life before the apocalypse.

Title: Conker's Bad Fur Day
Description: The vulgar adventures and exploits of a squirrel with a hangover, just trying to get back home while being forced to save the world.

Title: The Witcher 2: Assassins of Kings
Description: After being framed for a murder, a monster slayer must find the assassin and clear his name.

Title: Hitman: Blood Money
Description: A larger, more powerful agency is systematically eliminating assassins in a series of hits, who are all from Agent 47's contract killing firm, The International Contract Agency (ICA).

Title: Inside
Description: Hunted and alone, a boy finds himself drawn into the center of a dark project.

Title: Star Wars: Battlefront II
Description: Play as the foot soldier of the galaxy's greatest factions and wage war across countless planets.

Title: Blade Runner
Description: You play a blade runner investigating a series of violent replicant crimes, only to discover far more than you bargained for.

Title: Dead Space 2
Description: Set three years after the events of the first, Isaac Clarke's fight against a new Necromorph outbreak on the Sprawl, a space station above Saturn's largest moon, Titan.

Title: The Elder Scrolls III: Morrowind
Description: The protagonist travels by Morrowind, eastern province of the Septim Empire in Tamriel. He/she can save it from enslavement or explore for personal purposes.

Title: StarCraft II: Wings of Liberty
Description: Four years after the events of StarCraft: Brood War (1998), Jim Raynor fights against the Dominion and begins a search for artifacts when at the same time the Zerg attack once again.

Title: Kingudamu hâtsu: Bâsu bai surîpu
Description: Ten years before Sora held the Keyblade, three young Keyblade wielders bound by friendship, face being torn apart by the sinister monsters terrorizing other worlds and the manipulative mastermind behind them.

Title: Sly 2: La Banda dei Ladri
Description: Two years after defeating Clockwerk, Sly Cooper and his band of thieves must recover and destroy all of the stolen Clockwerk parts from a sinister organization before their old nemesis can return from the dead.

Title: Fainaru fantajî VIII
Description: A group of students at a military academy rescue a mysterious girl, who some say is the sorceress who wants to govern the universe.

Title: Fainaru fantajî IX
Description: When bandits try to kidnap the princess, they discover that it's the princess who wants to be kidnapped. But they are chased by an evil queen and an even more powerful entity.

Title: Metroid Prime
Description: A Space Pirate distress signal draws bounty hunter Samus Aran to Tallon IV, a world she discovers is being consumed by a terrible poison.

Title: Medieval II: Total War
Description: A diplomatic, strategic war game set between the years 1080 and 1530, focusing on medieval warfare, religion and politics in Europe, North Africa and the Middle East.

Title: Pokémon: Versione rossa
Description: Play as a young Pokémon trainer trying to catch all 150 Pokémon.

Title: Ratchet & Clank: Up Your Arsenal
Description: Ratchet and Clank return to the Solana Galaxy to combat Dr. Nefarious, a villain from Qwark's shady past, who wishes to turn all organic life into robots.

Title: Fire Emblem: Awakening
Description: During a turbulent era, Chrom, the prince of Ylisse and descendant of the Hero-King Marth, leads The Shepherds in observing and combating the bizarre activities of the neighboring country Plegia.

Title: Dragon Ball Z: Sparking! Meteor
Description: The third and final installment in the Budokai Tenkaichi series that includes the apocalyptic battles and the essence of the Dragon Ball series, following the main story.

Title: Age of Empires II: HD Edition
Description: The Age of Kings is set in the Middle Ages and contains thirteen playable civilizations.

Title: Pokémon Versione Argento
Description: Role playing game for the Game Boy Color, introducing the second generation of Pokémon, where you are on a quest to master Pokémon battling.

Title: Okami
Description: A cel-shaded action game set in feudal Japan, in which the wolf deity Amaterasu defends the land from evil forces.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Kamigami no toraifôsu 2
Description: Link is yet again tasked with restoring peace to the kingdom of Hyrule after a malevolent sorcerer named Yuga captures Princess Zelda and escapes through a rift to the ruined world of Lorule.

Title: Pokémon Versione Oro
Description: Role playing game for the Game Boy Advance, introducing the second generation of Pokémon, where you are on a quest to master Pokémon battling.

Title: Hogwarts Legacy
Description: Set during the late 1800s, a newly enrolled student at Hogwarts discovers that they possess the unusual ability to perceive and master Ancient Magic, becoming the key to an old secret that threatens to tear the wizarding world apart.

Title: Death Stranding
Description: Deliveryman Sam Porter must travel across a ravaged wasteland and reconnect the city states of America formed after a mysterious apocalyptic event dubbed 'death stranding' left the world in ruins and plagued by supernatural tar creatures.

Title: Resident Evil Village
Description: Ethan Winters' world suddenly comes crashing down when Chris Redfield's appearance sets off a chain of events that ultimately leads him to a mysterious village.

Title: L.A. Noire
Description: Cole Phelps, a war hero and rookie cop, moves up the ranks and solves dark cases in 1940s Los Angeles.

Title: Until Dawn
Description: A group of teenagers spend the weekend in a ski lodge on the anniversary of their friends' disappearance, unaware that they are not alone.

Title: Tomb Raider
Description: Armed with only the raw instincts and physical ability, experience Lara Croft's intense origin story from a young woman to a hardened survivor.

Title: Ratchet & Clank: Rift Apart
Description: They've travelled through space. They've travelled through time. Now, they'll have to travel through dimensions as their galaxy seems to rip itself apart. Ratchet and Clank must save the universe - again.

Title: Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag
Description: A video game where you play as sailor, privateer and assassin Edward Kenway exploring on and around the islands in the Caribbean Sea during the early 17th century.

Title: Halo 2
Description: As the alien Covenant invade Earth, the Master Chief must defend humanity's homeworld whilst discovering more about the rings called "Halo."

Title: Assassin's Creed: Brotherhood
Description: Desmond Miles continues to travel the memories of Ezio Auditore, bringing him to turn-of-the-century Rome with Ezio rebuilding the assassin order to bring down the tyrannical Borgia rule.

Title: The Walking Dead: The Game - Season 2
Description: Left to fend for herself, Clementine has been forced to learn how to survive in a world gone mad. Many months have passed and she is in search of safety.

Title: Super Mario RPG: Legend of the Seven Stars
Description: Just as Mario trounces Bowser for the millionth time, a giant, malevolent sword crashes into Bowser's keep, casting Mario, Princess Toadstool and Bowser far and wide, and breaking seven pieces from the wish-granting Star Road.

Title: Need for Speed: Most Wanted
Description: A lone street racer must use his talents to rise to the top of the Blacklist, comprised of the 15 most elite drivers in the city of Rockport.

Title: Horizon Zero Dawn: The Frozen Wilds
Description: Aloy's battle with the machines continues when she travels to The Cut, the home of the Banuk. There, she finds an AI that is being worshiped, and a mysterious 'Daemon' constantly attacking the Banuk.

Title: Cuphead
Description: An anthropomorphic cup embarks on a journey and fights a series of bosses to repay a debt to the devil.

Title: Gears of War 2
Description: Marcus Fenix and his COG Delta Squad fight against the Locust army to prevent them from sinking the cities of planet Sera.

Title: The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-Earth
Description: You play the events of The Lord of the Rings trilogy, both with the Fellowship of the Ring and the larger War of the Ring.

Title: Half-Life 2: Episode One
Description: Gordon Freeman and Alyx Vance must escape City 17 following the explosion of its fusion reactor.

Title: BioShock Infinite: Burial at Sea - Episode One
Description: 1958. After the events of BioShock Infinite (2013) and on the eve of the civil war that will destroy the underwater city, Elizabeth goes to Rapture to find Booker DeWitt and offers him her help to investigate the disappearance of an orphan girl.

Title: Mario Kart 64
Description: Nintendo's finest from the Mushroom Kingdom gather to race for first place in a multi-player mayhem classic for the Nintendo 64.

Title: Perfect Dark
Description: A female spy named Joanna Dark who received the highest grade ever from her spy training at Carrington Institute is sent to rescue a Doctor Caroll who sent a distress call to Carrington a few days before.

Title: StarCraft II: Heart of the Swarm
Description: After the events of StarCraft II: Wings of Liberty (2010), Sarah Kerrigan works to reunite the Zerg swarm in order to take revenge on Arcturus Mengsk.

Title: StarCraft II: Legacy of the Void
Description: After the events of StarCraft II: Heart of the Swarm (2013), Hierarch Artanis works to reunite the Protoss factions in order to retake their homeworld of Auir and stop Amon from destroying the galaxy.

Title: Crash Bandicoot: Warped
Description: Crash Bandicoot, Aku Aku and Coco travel through time to stop Dr. Cortex and Aku Aku's evil twin brother Uka Uka from enslaving Earth.

Title: Sam and Max Hit the Road
Description: Two screwball detectives are hired to track a couple of human oddities that went missing from a local Tourist Trap.

Title: Rome: Total War
Description: Rome: Total War is a strategy game set during the mid and late Roman Republic and early Roman Empire, with the player assuming control of one of three Roman families.

Title: Pokémon Versione Cristall
Description: A remake of the Gold and Silver versions of Pocket Monsters, with new animations, characters, and a new female trainer.

Title: Pokémon: Versione blu
Description: Play as a young Pokémon trainer trying to catch all 150 Pokémon.

Title: Grand Theft Auto III
Description: A young bank robber escapes from police custody and works his way up through the mafia ladder of crime-ridden Liberty City, USA.

Title: Max Payne 3
Description: The ex-cop turned private security guard for a wealthy family in Sao Paulo, Brazil finds himself thrown into a new deadly conflict.

Title: Lego Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga
Description: Play through all nine Star Wars films in a LEGO Game of epic proportions.

Title: Minecraft
Description: Welcome to the world of Minecraft where you can build, brew potions, enchant your armor and tools and adventure other biomes. Visit the Nether, or even defeat the Ender Dragon in the End.

Title: Bully
Description: A troubled teen is dropped off at the worst school in the country and must survive by rising through the rankings of the school system.

Title: Alien: Isolation
Description: In this first person survival horror adventure set fifteen years after the events of Alien (1979), Ripley's daughter becomes trapped on an alien-infested space station which holds answers to the mystery of her mother's disappearance.

Title: Resident Evil 7: Biohazard
Description: An ordinary man must embark on a search to find his missing wife that leads him to an abandoned house where a mysterious family lives who harbor an evil secret within the house and themselves.

Title: Grand Theft Auto IV: The Ballad of Gay Tony
Description: Luis Lopez is forced to help his boss Anthony "Gay Tony" Prince and clean up his mess, discovering that the rich life of Liberty City is just as dangerous as the tough streets where Luis grew up.

Title: Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy
Description: After an epic conflict known as the Galactic War swept through the cosmos. Star-Lord recently formed the Guardians of the Galaxy, they've been together for less than a year.

Title: Hellblade: Senua's Sacrifice
Description: Set in the age of Vikings, a broken Celtic warrior named Senua embarks on a haunting vision quest into Viking Hell to fight for the soul of her dead lover.

Title: Doom Eternal
Description: In this sequel to Doom (2016), Hell has taken Earth, so it's up to the Doom Slayer, the ultimate demon-killing machine created by a mystical force, to rip and tear the forces of Hell apart. However, Hell is not alone in this fight.

Title: Borderlands 2
Description: A new group of adventurers arrives on the frontier planet Pandora. They are assassinated by Handsome Jack, the most powerful merc on the planet. One of them survives and with the help of a deranged talking robot seeks loot and revenge.

Title: Halo: Reach
Description: A highly-trained branch of the UNSC known as the Noble Team must defend the planet of Reach from a massive Covenant invasion.

Title: Silent Hill 3
Description: Heather is suddenly thrust into a strange alternate reality filled with demonic imagery and twisted monsters. She quickly comes to find that the events unfolding around her have something to do with her past.

Title: Prince of Persia: Warrior Within
Description: A proud yet innocent prince is being chased by The Dahaka (Guardian of Time) as a consequence of his actions. He seeks aid from The Empress of Time to escape from the notion that he cannot change his fate.

Title: The Chronicles of Riddick: Escape from Butcher Bay
Description: Set before the events of Pitch Black (2000), this game tells the story of how Richard B. Riddick obtained his ability to see in the dark.

Title: Doom
Description: In the future, an unnamed marine fights for survival on a space station on Mars where the Union Aerospace Corporation accidentally opened up a physical portal to Hell.

Title: Little Nightmares II
Description: Little Nightmares II is a suspense-adventure game in which you play as Mono, a young boy trapped in a world that has been distorted by the humming transmission of a distant tower.

Title: What Remains of Edith Finch
Description: Edith Finch travels back to the Finch family home in Washington to explore her ancestral history after recent family events drive her to learn more about herself and the Finches.

Title: Command & Conquer: Red Alert 2
Description: You play either side of a new Allied/Soviet war when the real villian is an evil master of mind control.

Title: Splinter Cell: Chaos Theory
Description: Proving you can't keep a good agent down, Sam Fisher returns for this third undercover outing, which takes him deep inside North Korea on an information warfare mission.

Title: Biohazard 3: Last Escape
Description: Two months after surviving the grisly disaster at the mansion lab, Jill Valentine resigns from S.T.A.R.S. and attempts to escape the ruined nightmarish Racoon city.

Title: Forza Horizon 4
Description: Experience a shared world with dynamic seasons. Explore beautiful scenery, collect over 450 cars and become a Horizon Superstar in historic Britain. With highlight the super-car "McLaren Senna", in honor of Ayrton Senna.

Title: Deus Ex: Human Revolution
Description: After a shadowy black ops team kidnaps several scientists security manager Adam Jensen was sworn to protect, he must harness the power of his new-found cybernetic augmentations to save their lives.

Title: The Hyrule fantasy: Zeruda no densetsu
Description: Follows the story of a young boy named Link that must save a kidnapped princess from the evil, demonic Ganon, who put a spell on his lair which can only be removed with the 3 pieces of the Triforce, a golden triangle with mystical powers.

Title: Demon's Souls
Description: The great kingdom of Boletaria has fallen into disparity. King Allant has aroused the Old One from its long slumber, and a great fog descends upon the land, bringing forth great soul-devouring demons.

Title: Psychonauts
Description: Raz, a young psychic, must battle forces greater than he if he is to save his new-found friends at the Whispering Rock psychic camp, where children are having their brains mysteriously stolen.

Title: Celeste
Description: A young woman undertakes the challenge of climbing a mountain with dangerous perils and mysterious powers. Throughout her journey, she is confronted by Part Of Her, her bad side doppelgänger.

Title: Sly 3: Honor Among Thieves
Description: Sly Cooper and the gang must recruit a team of world-class thieves in order to penetrate his family vault of massive wealth and collect his inheritance before an evil genius retrieves it first.

Title: Full Throttle
Description: Framed for murdering a motorcycle magnate, a biker gang leader tries to clear his name and take revenge on the scheming businessman responsible.

Title: Ori and the Blind Forest
Description: Ori fell from the Spirit Tree in the forest of Nibel during a storm and was adopted by a bear-like creature named Naru, who raised Ori as her own.

Title: Il Signore degli Anelli: La Battaglia per la Terra di Mezzo II
Description: You play the Elf and the Dwarf nations as they fight their own battles against the forces of Sauron.

Title: Crash Team Racing
Description: In the fourth installment of the Crash Bandicoot series, an evil alien called Nitros Oxide challenges Crash, his friends, and even his enemies to a racing competition to see who is the fastest in the Universe.

Title: Donkey Kong Country
Description: Waking to find his banana hoard clean gone, Donkey Kong sets out with his nephew Diddy Kong through jungle and cavern, past temples and reef, across pine forests, factories, and mountains to rid the island of the wicked Kremlings and reclaim his bananas.

Title: Banjo-Kazooie
Description: The witch Gruntilda has captured Banjo's beloved sister, intending to leech the girl's youth and beauty through black magic and mad science. Banjo and Kazooie set out across nine worlds to get her back.

Title: Alice
Description: A game with an all new story that takes place after Lewis Carroll's stories. Alice must return to Wonderland and defeat the Queen of Hearts once and for all.

Title: Zeruda no densetsu: Yume o miru shima
Description: The ship in which Link travels back to Hyrule is destroyed in a storm. He awakens on a strange island, where he will find a new enemy and some new friends.

Title: Ico
Description: On a distant island, there is a legend that anyone born with horns will bring about calamity. When such a boy is locked away in a fortress, he must work together with a girl named Yorda to flee before they can be claimed by the spirits.

Title: Donkey Kong Country 2: Diddy's Kong Quest
Description: Kaptain K. Rool kidnaps Donkey Kong and imprisons him high atop Crocodile Isle. Diddy Kong and his friend Dixie Kong must brave pirate ships, volcanoes, swamps, demented theme parks and deep, dark forests to rescue the gormless gorilla.

Title: Super Smash Bros. Brawl
Description: The third Super Smash Bros. title, featuring a number of new additions, including an engrossing story mode and cooperative play, new characters, new stages, and online combat.

Title: Dreamfall: The Longest Journey
Description: Ten years past the inexplicable technological collapse of 2209, in a renewedly rallying future world, twenty-year-old Zoë must set out for a journey to help a friend expose an ultimate conspiracy that may be connected with the recurring visions she have been seeing lately.

Title: Warcraft II: Tides of Darkness
Description: The land of Azeroth is being attacked by evil orcs coming from the Dark Portal. Humans will have to fight for their country.

Title: Civilization IV
Description: Fourth installment in the turn-based strategy series Civilization, adding new tools to manage and expand your civilization, all-new easy to use mod capabilities and intense multiplayer modes and options.

Title: Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order
Description: Set shortly after Revenge of the Sith, the player takes on the role of a Jedi padawan being hunted by the Empire after Order 66.

Title: Fallout 4
Description: In the post-apocalyptic Boston, Massachusetts area, you play as the "Sole Survivor" of Vault 111, recently revived from centuries of forced cryostasis, determined to find your kidnapped son.

Title: Rise of the Tomb Raider
Description: Lara Croft continues her late father's research, trekking across Siberia in search of the answers her father couldn't find, facing off against an ancient and ruthless shadow organisation.
